## Usage

```bash
# Test connections
python anycost.py test

# Process single month
python anycost.py {{ provider.name }} --month 2024-08

# Process multiple months
python anycost.py {{ provider.name }} --months 2024-06,2024-07,2024-08

# Daily sync (yesterday's data)
python anycost.py daily

# Dry run (test without uploading)
python anycost.py {{ provider.name }} --month 2024-08 --dry-run
```
